course to earn a new certificate 
the course harris needs is similar to one he taught for 14 years 
at brooklyn college state rules require that he finish certain 
courses within 12 months on the job but harris has said he let the 
deadline pass because i couldnt see myself having to sit in a 
class that i taught 
the boards resolution passed unanimously said harris should 
