the word on the street is that georgette watsons 
head is worth 5000 if shes shot and doesnt die its 1000 
thats how badly street gangs want to get rid of the founder of 
dropadime a hot line that fields tips on drug pushers watson is 
under 24hour police surveillance and says she can accept that 
for now but she wont live in a fishbowl forever 
i want to be free she said wednesday they feel they can 
kill anyone who goes against their stance this is a fight not just 
for me but for the whole community if we take a stand now we 
wont have to pay later 
deputy superintendent william celester said police informants 
had received solid tips this week that local gang members had 
set a price on watsons life 
georgette watson has been getting various threats ever 
since she began to speak out about the drug dealers and everything 
else he said from time to time weve offered her police 
protection and shes always turned those offers down this time 
were insisting 
