a seasonally adjusted 7939 billion in october after remaining 
flat in september the september report was revised from a 02 
percent increase reported earlier and followed a 04 percent 
advance in august 
business sales meanwhile dropped 07 percent to a seasonally 
adjusted 5192 billion in october after falling a revised 07 
