ritters covenant house opened in 1969 after six teens showed up 
at his apartment looking for a place to stay the organization now 
has more than 1500 beds and serves about 25000 children annually 
more than 90 percent of its funding is private 
ritters group was one of 18 honored by president bush in april 
as winners of ronald reagan awards for volunteer excellence 
