holdings the company disclosed in the regulatory filing 
at 38 billion columbias junk bond holdings are the largest 
by far among the nations savings and loans they account for 40 
percent of the thrifts assets 
junk bonds are highyield highrisk securities prices paid for 
junk bonds have plunged in recent months amid fears of a recession 
and concerns about bonds that have been issued by troubled 
institutions 
